Belgian govt sets 80 bln bfr ' 97 austerity package . Belgium ' s 1997 budget will contain a total 80 billion Belgian francs austerity package , the government said in a policy statement on the budget . The 1997 package compares with 1996 ' s set of measures worth over 110 billion francs . - - Brussels Newsroom + 32 2 287 6810 , Fax + 32 2 230 7710 
